My mandate is to bring all of Norrath to heel and crush the opposition using guile, deceit, pestilence, agony, and Death.  When every land, Plane, and kingdom bows down in defeat before the God of Hate a new Age will begin and Darkness shall cover the earth.  Good shall be enslaved to Evil as Norrath becomes a vast pantry to sate the hunger of the Trolls... /Pusbag raises his royal scepter and roars into the night with rage... Server:  Druzzil Ro... Appearance:  Purple eyes, green warty skin, and long, leathery, pointed ears tipped with coarse hairs.</td></tr></table></td></tr></table></center>
